{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":988,"text":"Today I have just one request."},{"time":3983,"text":"Please don't tell me I'm normal."}]},{"cues":[{"time":7373,"text":"Now I'd like to introduce you to my brothers."},{"time":11749,"text":"Remi is 22,"},{"time":14015,"text":"tall and very handsome."},{"time":16979,"text":"He's speechless, but he communicates joy"},{"time":20907,"text":"in a way that some of the best orators cannot."},{"time":25190,"text":"Remi knows what love is."},{"time":27833,"text":"He shares it unconditionally and he shares it regardless."},{"time":32215,"text":"He's not greedy. He doesn't see skin color."},{"time":35735,"text":"He doesn't care about religious differences, and get this:"},{"time":39056,"text":"He has never told a lie."},{"time":42311,"text":"When he sings songs from our childhood,"},{"time":44792,"text":"attempting words that not even I could remember,"},{"time":47655,"text":"he reminds me of one thing:"},{"time":49879,"text":"how little we know about the mind, and how wonderful"},{"time":52432,"text":"the unknown must be."}]},{"cues":[{"time":56007,"text":"Samuel is 16. He's tall. He's very handsome."},{"time":61744,"text":"He has the most impeccable memory."},{"time":65528,"text":"He has a selective one, though."},{"time":68076,"text":"He doesn't remember if he stole my chocolate bar,"},{"time":71844,"text":"but he remembers the year of release for every song on my iPod,"},{"time":75134,"text":"conversations we had when he was four,"},{"time":77533,"text":"weeing on my arm on the first ever episode of Teletubbies,"},{"time":81004,"text":"and Lady Gaga's birthday."}]},{"cues":[{"time":84412,"text":"Don't they sound incredible?"},{"time":87149,"text":"But most people don't agree."},{"time":90173,"text":"And in fact, because their minds don't fit"},{"time":92909,"text":"into society's version of normal,"},{"time":95645,"text":"they're often bypassed and misunderstood."}]},{"cues":[{"time":98583,"text":"But what lifted my heart and strengthened my soul"},{"time":102349,"text":"was that even though this was the case,"},{"time":104669,"text":"although they were not seen as ordinary,"},{"time":107583,"text":"this could only mean one thing:"},{"time":110095,"text":"that they were extraordinary --"},{"time":113470,"text":"autistic and extraordinary."}]},{"cues":[{"time":117693,"text":"Now, for you who may be less familiar with the term \"autism,\""},{"time":122144,"text":"it's a complex brain disorder that affects social communication,"},{"time":126046,"text":"learning and sometimes physical skills."},{"time":129734,"text":"It manifests in each individual differently,"},{"time":132549,"text":"hence why Remi is so different from Sam."},{"time":135230,"text":"And across the world, every 20 minutes, one new person"},{"time":137864,"text":"is diagnosed with autism, and although it's one of"},{"time":140734,"text":"the fastest-growing developmental disorders in the world,"},{"time":143877,"text":"there is no known cause or cure."}]},{"cues":[{"time":147053,"text":"And I cannot remember the first moment I encountered autism,"},{"time":150318,"text":"but I cannot recall a day without it."},{"time":153397,"text":"I was just three years old when my brother came along,"},{"time":155782,"text":"and I was so excited that"},{"time":158046,"text":"I had a new being in my life."},{"time":161149,"text":"And after a few months went by,"},{"time":163878,"text":"I realized that he was different."},{"time":166263,"text":"He screamed a lot."},{"time":168469,"text":"He didn't want to play like the other babies did,"},{"time":171556,"text":"and in fact, he didn't seem"},{"time":173502,"text":"very interested in me whatsoever."},{"time":176387,"text":"Remi lived and reigned in his own world, with his own rules,"},{"time":180367,"text":"and he found pleasure in the smallest things,"},{"time":182573,"text":"like lining up cars around the room"},{"time":185096,"text":"and staring at the washing machine"},{"time":186773,"text":"and eating anything that came in between."},{"time":190155,"text":"And as he grew older, he grew more different,"},{"time":193900,"text":"and the differences became more obvious."},{"time":196583,"text":"Yet beyond the tantrums and the frustration"},{"time":200035,"text":"and the never-ending hyperactivity"},{"time":202804,"text":"was something really unique:"},{"time":205396,"text":"a pure and innocent nature, a boy who saw the world"},{"time":209364,"text":"without prejudice, a human who had never lied."},{"time":214995,"text":"Extraordinary."}]},{"cues":[{"time":218076,"text":"Now, I cannot deny that there have been"},{"time":219863,"text":"some challenging moments in my family,"},{"time":222595,"text":"moments where I've wished that they were just like me."},{"time":225708,"text":"But I cast my mind back to the things that they've taught me"},{"time":228492,"text":"about individuality and communication and love,"},{"time":232332,"text":"and I realize that these are things that"},{"time":235669,"text":"I wouldn't want to change with normality."},{"time":240067,"text":"Normality overlooks the beauty that differences give us,"},{"time":245220,"text":"and the fact that we are different doesn't mean that one of us is wrong."},{"time":248549,"text":"It just means that there's a different kind of right."},{"time":252387,"text":"And if I could communicate just one thing to Remi"},{"time":256204,"text":"and to Sam"},{"time":258530,"text":"and to you,"},{"time":260257,"text":"it would be that you don't have to be normal."},{"time":264053,"text":"You can be extraordinary."},{"time":268036,"text":"Because autistic or not,"},{"time":270117,"text":"the differences that we have --"},{"time":272327,"text":"We've got a gift! Everyone's got a gift inside of us,"},{"time":276695,"text":"and in all honesty, the pursuit of normality"},{"time":280159,"text":"is the ultimate sacrifice of potential."},{"time":283156,"text":"The chance for greatness, for progress and for change"},{"time":287496,"text":"dies the moment we try to be like someone else."}]},{"cues":[{"time":291375,"text":"Please -- don't tell me I'm normal."},{"time":294607,"text":"Thank you. (Applause)"},{"time":297080,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}